{"lead_id": "db351365-d56a-578e-abd9-b60ab0b35a41", "domain": "kintu.co", "company": {"name": "Chris Osborne | Founder of KintuLabs", "description": "[ Skip to content](https://kintu.co/#content)\n#  [Chris Osborne ](https://kintu.co)\n[ ](https://twitter.com/kintulabs)\n## Father | Investor | Developer\n![](https://kintu.co/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/header.jpg)\nI\u2019ve spent the past 20 years building and designing great web products, and have spent the past few years digging deep into building web apps with AI. Each month I share a short list of the most impactful AI tools I\u2019m playing with. It\u2019s short, and you can always cancel with one click:\n* * *\n### About Chris\nI\u2019ve spent over 20 years building web apps.\nHere\u2019s a few projects I\u2019m currently working on:\n  * [AstroSend](https://astrosend.com) \u2013 send email newsletters with AI\n  * [AI Startup Data](https://aistartupdata.com) \u2013 a database of recent AI startup funding deals\n  * [Urgent Jets](https://urgentjets.com) \u2013 a marketplace for last-minute private jet charters\n  * [Build Intent](https://buildintent.com) \u2013 learn how to build web apps with AI\n  * [Lead Orbit](https://leadorbit.xyz) \u2013 helping startups earn more revenue with email outreach\n  * [Thirsty Jobs](https://thirstyjobs.com) \u2013 a job board for the hospitality industry\n  * [Startup Names](https://startupnames.xyz) \u2013 great domain names for web startups\n  * [AI Depot](https://aidepot.co) \u2013 one of the biggest AI tool directories online\n  * [25Mins](https://25mins.xyz) \u2013 a super simple pomodoro timer I use every day\n\n\nI\u2019m happily married (16 years) and we have 2 boys together. We split our time between Hong Kong, Japan and Thailand.\nOutside of work and family time, I enjoy sailing, long walks, aviation, MMA, poker, old wines, and great coffee.\nThe less I own, the happier I become.\n* * *\nSubscribe to my [weekly newsletter \u2192](https://kintu.co/newsletter/)\n", "i